Package emissary.util

Class GitRepositoryState

  • java.lang.Object
    • emissary.util.GitRepositoryState
  • public class GitRepositoryState
extends Object
    POJO for parsing and returning values from a git properties file. The properties file is created during the maven build process by the git-commit-id-maven-plugin
